schema.name: DIVISOR
schema.comment: What we should divide the inventory number by

kind.value: CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(ioupmj)) IS NULL OR TRIM(ioupmj) = '' OR TRIM(ioupmj) = '0' THEN NULL ELSE to_timestamp(date_add(cast(substring(ioupmj+ 1900000,1,4) AS Date),cast(substring(ioupmj,4,3) as int)-1)) end

CASE WHEN LOWER(TRIM(iommej)) IS NULL OR TRIM(iommej) = '' OR TRIM(iommej) = '0' THEN NULL ELSE to_timestamp(date_add(cast(substring(iommej+ 1900000,1,4) AS Date),cast(substring(iommej,4,3) as int)-1)) end
CASE WHEN Length(Trim(IMDSC2)) = 0 THEN Trim(IMDSC1) ELSE CONCAT(Trim(IMDSC1),';',Trim(IMDSC2)) END
